user.biography: Explore a Galaxy of exclusive services – like Samsung Free, Samsung TV Plus, Galaxy Store, and more. Follow us to get the most out of your device.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by My Samsung Apps on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Lucky Dog abc NEWSLIVE STORIES BY amc BAYWATCH SAMSUNG WILDLife WILD CRIME CRIME3 360 BROUGHT ARE OCBSN vevo country mmoonbug Kids ds KITCHEN THE MOVIE HUB'.

node.text: Watch what you want, when you want, all at no cost. Browse Samsung TV Plus right from Samsung Free through the 🔗 in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by My Samsung Apps on July 26, 2021. May be an image of food and text that says 'Pay GROUPON'.

node.text: Score some great deals at local stores with Groupon and get up to 10% cash back while you’re at it. Boom. Learn more through the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by My Samsung Apps on July 20, 2021 tagging @angrybirds. May be a cartoon of text that says 'ANGRY BIRDS Available on Galaxy Store'.

node.text: The birds are back, and this time, they’re bigger, badder, and… birdier. Check out @AngryBirds 2, the sequel to one of the most popular mobile games of all time. Sling birds, smash pigs, and claim glorious victory. Play now through the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by My Samsung Apps on July 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, screen and text that says 'GAME PASS Galaxy Store'.

node.text: Galaxy Store is the only place to find exclusive deals on top games. Click the 🔗 in bio to head there and save on in-game purchases with coupons you can’t find anywhere else.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by My Samsung Apps on July 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, body of water and text that says 'Pay Expedia'.

node.text: Taking a grand adventure this summer? Get cash back on hotels and flights while you journey with Expedia. It’s basically getting rewarded to travel. Sweet. Learn more with the 🔗 in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by My Samsung Apps on June 24, 2021 tagging @vice. May be an image of text.

node.text: @VICE was just added. Watch the stories no one is willing to tell with premium series, documentaries, and more. Start watching for free! Learn more through the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by My Samsung Apps on June 21, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Prime Day deals. Cash back rewards. Pay amazon'.

node.text: Snag some of the best deals of the year on #PrimeDay and get cash back while you’re at it. Purchase any of Amazon’s top 20 products on June 21-22 for instant cash back rewards. Link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by My Samsung Apps on June 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'News Entertainment Sports Tech Business Surprise discovery buried in 500 million years of meteorite impacts on Earth Science Alert ago BTS wins best POP VMA, proving there's literally nothing they can't do BBC News hours ago Chris Paul's wife: Jada Crawley Clutch ClutchPoin Po Is 15 hours ago'.

node.text: Tap into news that matters to you with Samsung Free. Head to the 🔗 in bio to access articles on topics like local and global current events, entertainment, sports and more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by My Samsung Apps on June 10, 2021 tagging @leagueoflegends, and @playwildrift. May be a cartoon of 2 people and text that says 'Available on Galaxy Store LEAGUE LEGENDS WILDRIFT'.

node.text: Two of Runeterra's greatest swordmasters are headed to @playwildrift! Unlock either Irelia or Riven for free, and complete their mission path to earn icons, Poro coins, and more. Do you have the will to reforge what was broken? Play now through the link in our bio.

node.text: You deserve a win—wherever, whenever. The Play tab in Samsung Free is home to a galaxy of download-free, instantly playable games perfect for a quick gaming break. Game on at the 🔗 in bio.

node.text: Retro is back! Watch CINEVAULT: 80s now on Samsung TV Plus! Download the app at the 🔗 in bio for epic movies from the whole decade.
